{"tid":1681453,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有個好奇怪嘅trend","createTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T01:36:46.000Z","uid":30506,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bd116404336a925691681d0d2e611b653bb60417","tid":1681453,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"就係「冇人講？」<br />\n每個人有嘢想講就係問人做乜唔講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪鬥快定比賽 我又可唔可以話返嗰啲樓主做咩唔早一日就講<br />\n好似每日打開連登就係隨時要畀人責備咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BsckhGn/EB1-F754-C-A5-F8-4-A98-B85-E-CB45-F976-DAFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FBsckhGn%2FEB1-F754-C-A5-F8-4-A98-B85-E-CB45-F976-DAFF.jpg&h=14864664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n媽呀 好攰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 非分化 但係呢啲時候預其講晦氣說話 不如正正經經開post <br />\n唔好將互屌當日常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c306b9a46af3ba10f44bc8a0203d8dfe82c5d7e","tid":1681453,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e6ac21738396732285d576fc7bc7d7402acc278","tid":1681453,"uid":136893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9735953f7e8d8aed329780d750791c77035cd60","tid":1681453,"uid":98993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26975f2379df3e43f12150fa9a309b05b971597c","tid":1681453,"uid":61484,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"xxxx冇人講<br />\nxxxx已成condom<br />\n再係咁就輸<br />\nxx都唔做仲點贏"},{"pid":"9db9c7e7d63c91b9976beb22c5a84bf6df556e41","tid":1681453,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"你部iphone咁長既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6e9adce4e2da3cf6f142160bfcfdbcd888a481","tid":1681453,"uid":292497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"咁連登既奇怪trend有無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e44e342faa68e64776604dbfb1dc0a5b0f1b14","tid":1681453,"uid":212473,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"唔係連登，係因為中國人劣根性。<br />\n受到上一代父母，長輩，老師，公司，影響<br />\n香港人好鍾意用呢種方式表達"},{"pid":"6154a52e25b609f995d6c7dd64cd46e6e80e6640","tid":1681453,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9db9c7e7d63c91b9976beb22c5a84bf6df556e41","tid":1681453,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"你部iphone咁長既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"咁你都發現到 好野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e74233b67f00eea2821a8712a49fec1abc5a273","tid":1681453,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi